From: Laurent Pinchart <laurent.pinchart+renesas@ideasonboard.com>
Date: Wed, 17 May 2017 02:20:07 +0300
Subject: drm: rcar-du: Map memory through the VSP device
Git-commit: fa5b4114202de0c1a7a64fd407af0b81ca529419
Patch-mainline: v4.13-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

For planes handled by a VSP instance, map the framebuffer memory through
the VSP to ensure proper IOMMU handling.

